      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">3.103-1</ph> Solicitation provision.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d87e8" class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.203-2.dita#FAR_52_203_2"
                  base="i1063268"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.203-2</xref>, Certificate of Independent Price Determination, in solicitations when a firm-fixed-price contract or fixed-price contract with economic price adjustment is contemplated, unless-</p>
         <ol id="d85e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d87e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The acquisition is to be made under the simplified acquisition procedures in <xref href="Part_13.dita#FAR_Part_13"
                        base="i1112458"
                        outputclass="fm:Part"
                        class="- topic/xref ">partÂ  13</xref>;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d87e23">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d87e28">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            The solicitation is a request for technical proposals under two-step sealed bidding procedures; or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d87e33">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
						            The solicitation is for utility services for which rates are set by law or regulation.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
